<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，昨天擔任<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聖誕老人的助手，<delay20 />真是辛苦你了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聖誕禮物中充滿了<delay20 />
聖誕老人和你的溫柔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這可是我的寶物喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要一想到你昨天送來的<delay20 />
那個來自聖誕老人的禮物<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就高興到忍不住反覆端詳呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天真是謝謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能收到你送的聖誕禮物，<delay20 />
我覺得非～常高興喔<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧有你，<delay frames="40" />今年的平安夜
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />成為了我最棒的回憶，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay20 />
聖誕快樂！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你<delay20 />昨天送的禮物。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能跟你交換禮物<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是我最棒的回憶喔。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />謝謝你。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖說昨天本就是名為平安夜的<delay20 />
特別日子<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是在收到<delay20 />來自你和聖誕老人的禮物後，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />變成了更加意義非凡的節日喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的聖誕快樂<delay20 />
就是指這種感覺吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />除了聖誕老人的禮物之外，<delay20 />
還能收到你送的禮物，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這讓我的內心被愛給填滿了喔。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來我來得及在聖誕節結束前
向你傳達這件事，<delay20 /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「聖誕快樂！」<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是我想傳達的事喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這些聖誕禮物<delay20 />
能作為紀念品來保留回憶，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我是不會拘泥於物質的喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能在聖誕節這種特別的日子裡<delay20 />
見到<tag a="110" b="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是這樣我就很幸福了。</message>
</msbt>